Package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.cell.message

Class GeocasterResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.cell.message.GeocasterResult
  • public class GeocasterResult
extends Object
    The message that comes out of the Geocaster and is intended for the Downstream module. It contains information about the Unicast/Multicast mode and the accordingly casted receiver(s) in their current region.
